  "What is a 'Riemann sum'?": "什么叫\"Riemann总和\"?",
  "The exact value of an integral": "积分的准确值",
  "A method for finding derivatives": "寻找衍生物的方法",
  "The limit of a sequence": "序列的极限",
  "An approximation of a definite integral by summing areas of rectangles": "将矩形区域分布成一整块,近似于一个明确的整体整体",
  "A Riemann sum approximates the area under a curve using rectangles. As the number of rectangles approaches infinity, the sum converges to the definite integral.": "Riemann总和使用矩形接近曲线下的区域。随着矩形数接近无穷,总和会与确定的整体体相融合。",
  "What is a 'definite integral'?": "什么是\"无限整体\"?",
  "The derivative of the area function": "区域函数的衍生物",
  "The antiderivative evaluated at one point": "在某一点被评估的抗降解剂",
  "The limit of Riemann sums as n approaches infinity; represents the signed area under a curve": "Riemann 总和的上限为 n 接近无穷;表示曲线下的签名区域",
  "An integral without limits": "完整性,无限制",
  "The definite integral from a to b of f(x) dx is the limit of Riemann sums and represents the signed area between f(x) and the x-axis.": "f(x) dx的a至b的确定有机体是Riemann 金额的限度,代表 f(x) 和 x轴之间的签名区域。",
  "What is the difference between 'left' and 'right' Riemann sums?": "\"左\"和\"右\"之间有什么区别?",
  "Left always underestimates; right always overestimates": "左总是低估;右总是高估",
  "Left uses narrower rectangles": "左用较窄矩形",
  "They give the same result": "产生同样的结果",
  "Left uses the left endpoint of each subinterval for rectangle height; right uses the right endpoint": "左对矩形高度使用每个次对数的左端端点;右对右对端点使用右对端点",
  "Left Riemann sums evaluate f at the left endpoint, right sums at the right endpoint of each subinterval. For increasing functions, left underestimates and right overestimates.": "Left Riemann 总和在左端点对 f 进行估测,在每个次间隔的右端点对右端点进行估测。 对于增加的函数, 左偏小和右高估 。",
  "What does 'signed area' mean?": "“签署区域”是什么意思?",
  "Area to the right is positive": "权利区域是积极的",
  "Area above the x-axis is positive; area below is negative": "X轴上方的面积为正数;下方为负数",
  "All area is positive": "所有区域均为正数",
  "The integral is always positive": "整体始终是积极的",
  "Definite integrals compute signed area: regions where f(x) > 0 contribute positive area, and regions where f(x) < 0 contribute negative area.": "直线构件计算签名区域:f(x) > 0贡献积极区域;f(x) < 0贡献负区域。",
  "What does 'partition' mean in the context of Riemann sums?": "在Riemann的金额中,“分配”意味着什么?",
  "Breaking the function into pieces": "将函数折断成碎片",
  "Separating variables": "分离变量",
  "Finding critical points": "寻找关键点",
  "Dividing the interval [a, b] into n subintervals": "将间隔 [a, b] 分切为 n 次间隔",
  "A partition divides [a, b] into subintervals, typically of equal width Delta x = (b-a)/n, for computing Riemann sums.": "分区将 [a, b] 分隔为次隔年数,通常等宽为Delta x = (b-a)/n,用于计算Riemann总和。",
  "What is 'sigma notation' and how is it used in Riemann sums?": "“污名符号”是什么? 里曼数字是如何使用的?",
  "It's a way to write integrals": "这是写积分的一种方式",
  "It represents the limit": "代表上限",
  "It represents the product of terms": "它代表条款的产物",
  "Sigma (Σ) notation compactly writes the sum of rectangle areas: Σ f(x_i) * Delta x": "Sigma () 符号缩写矩形区域之和: * f(x_i) * Delta x",
  "Sigma notation writes the Riemann sum as Σ_{i=1}^{n} f(x_i*) Delta x, where x_i* is the sample point in the i-th subinterval.": "Sigma 符号将Riemann sum 写为 i=1n} f(x_i*) Delta x, 其中 x_i* 是 i-th 子隔热器中的样本点 。",
  "What does 'Delta x' represent in a Riemann sum?": "\"Delta x\"在Riemann总和中代表什么?",
  "The area of each rectangle": "每个矩形的面积",
  "The number of subintervals": "子对数数",
  "The width of each subinterval: (b - a) / n": "每个次间隔宽度:(b- a) / n",
  "The height of each rectangle": "每个矩形的高度",
  "Delta x = (b-a)/n is the width of each subinterval when the interval is divided into n equal parts.": "Delta x = (b-a)/n 是每个次interval的宽度, 当间隔被分为 n 等分时 。",
  "What is a 'sample point' in a Riemann sum?": "Riemann的提法中什么是“样点”?",
  "A point x_i* chosen from each subinterval to determine the rectangle height": "从每个次interval 中选择一个点 x_i *,以确定矩形高度",
  "The endpoint of the interval regardless of prevailing conditions": "不论普遍条件如何,间隔的终点",
  "The midpoint of [a, b] within the broader context of endpoint": "(a,b) 在更广泛的终点范围内的中点[a,b]中点",
  "The zero of the function, at least according to standard theory": "函数零,至少根据标准理论",
  "The sample point is the x-value chosen from each subinterval. Left endpoint, right endpoint, and midpoint are common choices.": "抽样点是从每个次interval中选择的 x 值。 左端点、 右端点和中点是常见的选择 。",
  "What happens to a Riemann sum as n approaches infinity?": "Riemann 和n的无穷会怎么样?",
  "It remains an approximation": "它仍然是近似",
  "It converges to the exact value of the definite integral": "它与确定整体的精确价值相吻合,",
  "It diverges to infinity": "它与无穷无穷",
  "It approaches zero": "它接近零",
  "As n -> infinity (and Delta x -> 0), the Riemann sum approaches the definite integral. This is the formal definition of the integral.": "作为 n - > 无穷( 和 Delta x - > 0) , Riemann 和 接近确定的整体。 这是对整体的正式定义 。",
  "What are the 'limits of integration'?": "融合的界限是什么?",
