  "The maximum and minimum of the function": "最高和最低功能",
  "The limits as x approaches a value": "x 接近值时的限值",
  "Limits of integration are the endpoints a (lower) and b (upper) that define the interval over which we integrate.": "整合的界限是确定我们整合间隔的终点a(低)和b(高)。",
  "An ecologist measures tree density along a 1-km transect at 200m intervals: 10, 15, 20, 18, 12 trees per meter. Using a left Riemann sum, estimate the total number of trees.": "生态学家用每米10, 15, 20, 18, 12棵树测量1公里横截面的树密度, 间隔为200米。 使用左翼Riemann总和, 估计树木的总数 。",
